===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A utensil, usually [[tubular]] in form, containing ink used to [[write]] or make marks.
#: ''He took notes with a '''pen'''.''
# A mark made with [[ink]].
#: ''I need some stain remover, this mark is in '''pen'''.''
# An [[enclose]]d area used to contain [[domesticated]] animals, especially [[sheep]] or [[cattle]].
#: ''There are two steers in the third '''pen'''.''
# {{baseball}} The [[bullpen]].
#: ''Two righties are up in the '''pen'''.''
# A female [[swan]].

